{"tid":2325185,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（滾回中国）繼越南後中国再在緬甸邊境建南方長城 嚴防中国人偷渡","createTime":"2020-12-14T12:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T00:59:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9da81d2109db40ab36ad3041887e63169d36ec52","tid":2325185,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:14:36.000Z","msg":"2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19，武漢肺炎）疫情爆發後，中國相繼傳出多起民眾偷渡到越南務工被捕的案件，原因是許多工廠因疫情停工以及外移到越南。中國今年為此在中越邊境修建鋼筋混凝土圍牆，防止國人偷渡。<br />\n<br />\n繼中越邊境後，緬甸北部果敢族官方推特12日發文指出，中國政府為防止本國公民偷渡外逃緬甸，代號「南方長城」的緬中邊境隔斷一期工程全部完工，長度660公里，全部由帶刺的鐵網拉成。<br />\n<br />\n文章並稱，二期工程將於明年底完工，屆時，緬中邊境2000多公里將全部隔斷。三期工程將於2022年10月完工，屆時重點偷渡路段將安裝高壓電網，所有地方將安裝天網監視系統以及紅外線報警系統。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3381216\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3381216&d=4UWfeJE2Id0Ic3Ynx8r7n0ZZ0ArqIWVBMBEeODt8eII%3D&h=cde7575f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3381216&h=f083a511\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3381216</a>"},{"pid":"65b1485cc504978a6a630fcf6a6c918fb5266d45","tid":2325185,"uid":287891,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:16:09.000Z","msg":"起牆永遠係用嚟擋自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f116d4081b0305a1c2ae90c4f7d73935e28f3d","tid":2325185,"uid":215634,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T14:30:44.000Z","msg":"萬里長城永不倒，千里黃河水滔滔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歌詞原來係真"},{"pid":"178477433c32a12bedd8db49ab7d2b5ac8c771e9","tid":2325185,"uid":36162,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T14:37:14.000Z","msg":"又唔見佢武肺個時唔俾人走<br />\n正仆街陷家鏟"},{"pid":"3eba1e617d0ff2fa5e99003c10a89b4a5025d86b","tid":2325185,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-1